This is a sample bank application to simulate a teller, bank admin and customer activities in a bank. 

The application allows users to register themselves and get a unique Account number as a customer of the bank. Allows admin to create tellers for the bank as well.
It features the transactional functionalities like withdrawal and deposit to customers accounts and finally allows users to view the transactions made so far.
Bill pay feature enables users to add payees from other banks to pay bills and view the payment history.
Customer accounts can be closed at any moment by the bank admin without any hassle.
Customers can update their details in the system and that implies that the Admin can do so as well.
